ike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:44:22.000Z","msg":"唔需要，香港係控方提出證據證明一個人犯法<br />\n辯方只需要證明控方嘅證據有疑點<br />\n呢個疑點只要係一個合理嘅可能性，唔需要證據"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:50:56.000Z","msg":"但放蛇呢個行為不嬲都有<br />\n之前既案例係點?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:56:41.000Z","msg":"放蛇係可以，但唔可以做主動角色<br />\n即係例如去啲按摩店問人打丁幾錢<br />\n你問左先就係entrapment<br />\n而家個情況係可能有警畜混入示威者之中帶頭搞事，其他人被動跟從<br />\n佢地甚至可能帶頭放火掉汽油彈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:00:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"975d612bb57142d9725b2cf7157011d03c6d3665","tid":1445683,"uid":124452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:00:27.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"44fb5aa6d4385e9924f0987caddc8cd09279248c","tid":1445683,"uid":272119,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:02:07.000Z","msg":"molamola，邊一區安全，落西鐵站有白衣人，太古同葵芳站內有催淚彈，北角有既人打平民。"},{"pid":"c445850582a2ead3c6a239ba526e2406e7a29f7a","tid":1445683,"uid":242779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a95519d7bf7fbb3d6706aed48563197f7eddda2a","tid":1445683,"uid":8076,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:59:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:02:46.000Z","msg":"有原片嘅你必需要確保你條片係原裝冇改動，片源一直係你自己保管之下並無比其他人掂到<br />\n要放上庭一定要條chain of evidence係冇其他人搞過<br />\n當然一般而言辯方無責任舉證"},{"pid":"22fbb10694eef66072e324d76f50c739ca40df9c","tid":1445683,"uid":242779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:03:17.000Z","msg":"推到啲畜牲瀨屎"},{"pid":"4c0c3369cae8a7700d38ebcd8fc71fb7e86f6071","tid":1445683,"uid":242779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:05:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f1308b4bb6a74d3552102d2091ed6f6c3137715","tid":1445683,"uid":279616,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:13:56.000Z","msg":"唔係仇警，大家一定要清楚知道點解要清算警隊。警暴（濫捕、濫告、不依法規）係暴政一部分，唔全面改革警隊、監警制度，只會令目前同將來爭取雙普選更加舉步維艱<br />\n<br />\n所以，絕對唔需要否認自己係針對警隊，針對警隊就係對準政權。唔通你淨係針對林鄭、唔針對政制，就會有雙普選？<br />\n<br />\n#罷工罷巿罷買<br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我參與全港三罷<br />\n#各區集會<br />\n#出核彈麻包袋都唔割蓆<br />\n#直至政府跪低<br />\n#抵制一切紅媒相關商業活動"},{"pid":"afcc8e7ef662a7e2b81854922d52e0d2e6f4ccee","tid":1445683,"uid":16792,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"acfc294167f03b18ed7c475a56b8d894b65572dc","tid":1445683,"uid":242779,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"55cbcebebc4233bb600ca3bf4eb26e47dad8d8ef","tid":1445683,"uid":170309,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"24590e3e135f9d6089734ebe5ccc3e4112ad203b","tid":1445683,"uid":242779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:26:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Entrapment\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FEntrapment&d=5YfG332q5u5uc%2FC0Cq16Reu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=46f94bff\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Entrapment</a><br />\n<br />\n香港<br />\n法理上，「釣魚執法」、「警方設陷」（Entrapment）由指當事人本無意圖違法，欲遭執法人員的引誘而犯罪。而香港只許通稱「放蛇」的執法現象，即「緝捕圈套」（sting operation），指當事人有犯罪意圖，而執法者設下圈套不涉及&quot;意圖犯罪，或意圖協助、教唆、慫使或促致犯罪&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n行政、執法部門曾假扮嫖客、妓女、賭客或其他顧客等隱蔽身份，待當事人從事違法行為時揭露身份，將其抓捕的例子。放蛇行動包括警察假扮妓女，將嫖客逮捕，以及假扮嫖客，在答應性交易後將妓女逮捕的行為。但若警察的確與妓女發生性行為（因參與犯罪，涉及&quot;意圖犯罪，或意圖協助、教唆、慫使或促致犯罪&quot;的問題。），則根據香港法例，不能對該妓女予以起訴。2019年有報導指，香港有酒吧發生涉向顧客提供「揸波遊戲」，並拘捕涉案人。這案例引起多項來自社會和法律界的爭議，包括「不合理的放蛇次數」、揸胸屬否「性服務」犯罪的爭議等。[24][25]此外，也有警察假意購買毒品，然後抓捕毒販。<br />\n-----------------<br />\n如果有片影到卧底掉汽油彈/衝/攻擊警畜等等行為，係唔能夠對在場人士起訴<br />\n無論佢地係咪帶頭果個，有份做都係entrapment,香港法律係唔容許的<br />\n警渣唔知邊個諗埋啲柒撚懞懞屎橋啦<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母黑警死全家，你地啲仔女都會比天收</span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:35:07.000Z","msg":"上到court如果指出係俾卧底叫佢咁，全部入唔到"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:39:33.000Z","msg":"no, 被告上庭唔需要自己答辯<br />\n自己律師指出可能有卧底混入示威者投放汽油彈/帶頭衝擊就夠<br />\ncreate reasonable doubt<br />\n而家有晒證據係有卧底混入去<br />\n有咩暴力行為都係卧底entrapment"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:14:03.000Z","msg":"最後疑點利益歸與被告，罪名不成立。"},{"pid":"08bf8f20d38a11fa0fb3d33e19f70e85db49acb0","tid":1445683,"uid":187141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:15:00.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"335c7525ffa6eabe0e9a3269d5609726cb2267c6","tid":1445683,"uid":16792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b597c8514475a96a5b5b19071b42466ec5083eaf","tid":1445683,"uid":242779,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:47:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我知你班仆街黑警係到Mon緊Post,出番去啦，呢啲法律嘢你地唔識㗎啦，警例讀熟啲了解自己既權力同限制先啦柒頭</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:15:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6366c9864b35fd4a19f06362e1f9d8625952c319","tid":1445683,"uid":214952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:15:41.000Z","msg":"屌有撚嬲 佢地仲有咩做唔出"},{"pid":"aaafb66127af55787cd78db7324681bd607d17cc","tid":1445683,"uid":16792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28b209888262d41a0cc62253d8c53d56d5562b7b","tid":1445683,"uid":33543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:49:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MQZURP7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMQZURP7.jpg&h=e8ff53ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BvexDu8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBvexDu8.jpg&h=6025e5fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cnQpuBP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcnQpuBP.jpg&h=bdc91acf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Product should only be used outdoors. <br />\n<br />\nDo not fire directly at personnel</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記者會上話會跟足廠商指引而無必要親身試彈，宜家冇跟指引就有必要親身試啦？</span><br />\n<br />\n間廠叫NonLethal Technology, 有冇人去提醒下間廠再培訓垃圾狗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nonlethaltechnologies.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nonlethaltechnologies.com%2F&d=5YfG332q5u5uc%2FC0Cq16Reu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=3cdfce53\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nonlethaltechnologies.com/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:15:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4c605e4938f16749bc3a3a7ff1a9f7baf2c51bfc","tid":1445683,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:16:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我估林鄭個劇本係<br />\n搵解放軍混入示威者殺一兩隻狗<br />\n靠first blood黎民意翻盤</span>"},{"pid":"cb9972c71e8c10861f6889e643cc85980d874743","tid":1445683,"uid":123111,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"acfc294167f03b18ed7c475a56b8d894b65572dc","tid":1445683,"uid":242779,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"55cbcebebc4233bb600ca3bf4eb26e47dad8d8ef","tid":1445683,"uid":170309,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"24590e3e135f9d6089734ebe5ccc3e4112ad203b","tid":1445683,"uid":242779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:26:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Entrapment\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FEntrapment&d=5YfG332q5u5uc%2FC0Cq16Reu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=46f94bff\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Entrapment</a><br />\n<br />\n香港<br />\n法理上，「釣魚執法」、「警方設陷」（Entrapment）由指當事人本無意圖違法，欲遭執法人員的引誘而犯罪。而香港只許通稱「放蛇」的執法現象，即「緝捕圈套」（sting operation），指當事人有犯罪意圖，而執法者設下圈套不涉及&quot;意圖犯罪，或意圖協助、教唆、慫使或促致犯罪&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n行政、執法部門曾假扮嫖客、妓女、賭客或其他顧客等隱蔽身份，待當事人從事違法行為時揭露身份，將其抓捕的例子。放蛇行動包括警察假扮妓女，將嫖客逮捕，以及假扮嫖客，在答應性交易後將妓女逮捕的行為。但若警察的確與妓女發生性行為（因參與犯罪，涉及&quot;意圖犯罪，或意圖協助、教唆、慫使或促致犯罪&quot;的問題。），則根據香港法例，不能對該妓女予以起訴。2019年有報導指，香港有酒吧發生涉向顧客提供「揸波遊戲」，並拘捕涉案人。這案例引起多項來自社會和法律界的爭議，包括「不合理的放蛇次數」、揸胸屬否「性服務」犯罪的爭議等。[24][25]此外，也有警察假意購買毒品，然後抓捕毒販。<br />\n-----------------<br />\n如果有片影到卧底掉汽油彈/衝/攻擊警畜等等行為，係唔能夠對在場人士起訴<br />\n無論佢地係咪帶頭果個，有份做都係entrapment,香港法律係唔容許的<br />\n警渣唔知邊個諗埋啲柒撚懞懞屎橋啦<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母黑警死全家，你地啲仔女都會比天收</span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:35:07.000Z","msg":"上到court如果指出係俾卧底叫佢咁，全部入唔到"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:39:33.000Z","msg":"no, 被告上庭唔需要自己答辯<br />\n自己律師指出可能有卧底混入示威者投放汽油彈/帶頭衝擊就夠<br />\ncreate reasonable doubt<br />\n而家有晒證據係有卧底混入去<br />\n有咩暴力行為都係卧底entrapment"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:16:54.000Z","msg":"agree，利申法律撚 唔係讀law但係學過相關法律"},{"pid":"f5630e640367303bff468f5c35eb446380060425","tid":1445683,"uid":62889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:19:51.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>11/8</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 射頭<br />\n2. 721無起訴<br />\n3. 狗扮示威者<br />\n4. 室內射tear gas</span>"},{"pid":"7769029a42cc11f163759789ccfc8242a79851ec","tid":1445683,"uid":242779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c605e4938f16749bc3a3a7ff1a9f7baf2c51bfc","tid":1445683,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:16:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我估林鄭個劇本係<br />\n搵解放軍混入示威者殺一兩隻狗<br />\n靠first blood黎民意翻盤</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:23:59.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦，畜牲死幾多隻我都唔撚心痛<br />\n我心痛香港人受傷<br />\n果班畜牲就算比人殺全家，我當同平時劏豬劏牛一樣，唔會有感覺<br />\n豬牛死左我都會尊敬佢地饅飽左人類<br />\n呢班禽獸不如畜物不如嘅兩腳生物，我諗佢地同小強一樣死幾多都冇人care,最好係呢個世界上消失<br />\n我唔係講緊香港唔需要警察<br />\n係唔需要呢班不知所謂嘅垃圾做警察"},{"pid":"2e764dad2a60737e64b80ed244f9c22edcd69263","tid":1445683,"uid":242779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:26:00.000Z","msg":"總之一句講晒<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">出核彈都唔割蓆，因為全部都係警畜卧底做，香港示威者全部奉公守法</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a5e6552ff78e8c88a510ce79de2079597879391d","tid":1445683,"uid":242779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:28:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df31c409570d53bf50f80afb1cd9a03ce65300e0","tid":1445683,"uid":242779,"lik